title: Prince
content:
Prince may refer to:

  • Frog prince, encountered in the Kiss the frog random event if the player is female
  • Prince Ali Rescue, a free-to-play quest
    • Prince Ali, the son of the Emir whom players have to rescue from Lady Keli in Prince Ali Rescue
  • Prince Anlaf, ruler of Burthorpe
  • Prince black dragon, a pet obtained from killing the King Black Dragon
  • Prince Brand, the son of King Vargas whom female players marry during the Throne of Miscellania quest
  • Prince leggings, male clothing from the frogs' random event
  • Prince outfit, male clothing from the frogs' random event
  • Prince tunic, male clothing from the frogs' random event
  • Slug Prince, encountered and slew during The Slug Menace quest
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
